<div style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 550px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; border-radius: 12px; background-color: #ffffff;">

  <h2 style="color: #4f46e5; margin-top: 0; font-size: 24px;">Hi, <%= @subscriber.name %>!</h2>

  <p>Thanks for your interest in <a href="https://pasabaya.app" target="_blank"><strong>Pasabaya.app</strong></a>.</p>

  <p>I’m Artem, a student at UPOU. I’m building this project because I know how frustrating the daily commute can be in the Philippines. My goal isn't to build a transport company, but simply to provide a more convenient way to find travel companions than scrolling through disorganized Facebook groups or Reddit threads.</p>

  <p>With the recent declaration of an <strong>energy emergency</strong>, there is a clear need for us to be more efficient and travel together. Pasabaya.app is just an organized tool to help you find someone heading your way.</p>

  <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px;">
    <p style="margin-top: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #374151;">What’s coming next?</p>
    <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 0;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong>A short video:</strong> I’m preparing a simple video to show how the platform works. It’s just a screen share so you can see the idea in action.</li>
      <li><strong>Facebook Group:</strong> I’ll be setting up a dedicated group soon so we can share feedback and stay connected.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>I value your time. I’ll only email you when there’s a major update or when we’re ready to launch the platform.</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 35px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
    Talk soon,<br>
    <strong style="color: #111827;">Artem Blazhievskii</strong><br>
    MIS Student, UPOU | Owner & CTO of Pasabaya.app
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
    <em>Pasabaya.app is a student-led, open-source volunteer project.</em>
  </div>
  <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
    Changed your mind?
    <%= link_to "Unsubscribe from this list",
                unsubscribe_subscriber_url(@subscriber.signed_id(purpose: :unsubscribe)),
                target: "_top",
                style: "color: #6366f1; text-decoration: underline;" %>
  </p>
</div>